Now, I'm focusing on "Xã Phú Nhuận" and its status within the new province of "Tỉnh Vĩnh Long," or specifically, "Thành phố Bến Tre" (which is now part of Vĩnh Long). I'll analyze the relevant resolutions from the government to trace any changes.
